name: Secret Agent Xin Zhao
description: Most people who come into contact with Xin Zhao have a gap in their memory where the encounter once was. This is probably for the best as most encounters he's involved in tend to include close encounters of the third kind, protecting civilians against terrifying extraterrestrial invaders, or evading aggressive UFO dive bombers.
